snippet.title: PROLOGUE TRAILER | Kill/Cure: Beautiful Vice
snippet.description:
We hope we were able to excite you.
Take part in our Q&A on the discord, 
if you want to have a chance of being shown in a future video where we’ll be answering all your questions.
More infos can be found on the discord.
